				<h1>book tagged</h1>
				
					<p>Swaroop book tagged me so, here goes the list &#8211; <br />
<strong>Total number of books I own</strong> :<br />
More than 300. A motley  collection of tech books, novels, management books, sci-fi, self-help books, kannada novels, plays and  philosophy.  I buy most of my books second-hand, although I&#8217;m not averse to spending quite a bit of money on books I want to collect. </p>

	<p><strong>The last book bought?</strong>: <br />
three actually &#8211; I,Robot by Isac Asimov, The Hobbit by JRR Tolkien, ಕನ್ನಡ ಸಾಹಿತ್ಯ ಚರಿತ್ರೆ -ರಂ.ಶ್ರೀ.ಮುಗಳಿ.  (History of Kannada Literature by R.M.Mugali)</p>

	<p><strong>The last book you read?</strong> :  I,Robot by Isac Asimov</p>

	<p><strong>Books I am currently reading</strong> : Lila &#8211; an inquiry in morals by Robert Pirsig &#38; ಟೀಕೆ,ಟಪ್ಪಣಿ &#8211; ಪಿ.ಲಂಕೇಶ್. (a collection of essays/editorials by P.Lankesh).</p>

	<p><strong>Books that mean a lot to me</strong> : ( <a href="http://btbytes.com/pradeep/4/my-book-o-rama">no way a complete list</a> )</p>

